<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - yạlly ḥbk nwʿ tạny jytny wgẖyrt zmạny
 gẖyrt qlby bqlb jdyd wṣạrt ạlsmạ hy mkạny
 1- zmạn ạlḥb mḍy̱ lạ myn ysạ̉l wlạ fy ṣdy̱
 ạsrʿt ly fy ạ̹ḥtyạjy ạṣbḥt ạ̉nạ mlkk fy tẖwạny
 2- sqytny nbʿ ạlkẖlạṣ mn ạydk mạ ạḥly̱ ạlạ̹kẖlạṣ
 mʿrwfk ly ạlạ̉wl wmʿrwfk ly tạny
 3- gẖfrt bqlbk ạlkbyr wsạmḥt dẖnby ạlʿẓym
 kẖṭwẗ ʿmry msẖwạr ṭwyl wạlḥryẗ hy nysẖạny</lyrics>
<title>yạlly ḥbk</title>
</song>